nodes.text: Vader - Dark Visions 5 is the fifth and final issue of the canon comic book miniseries Star Wars: Vader - Dark Visions. It was written by Dennis "Hopeless" Hallum, illustrated by Geraldo Borges, and published on June 12, 2019 by Marvel Comics.

NIGHTMARE ON THE OUTER RIM! A backwater jungle planet teeming with poisonous plants. The search for a device that can track the REBELS. A psychedelic nightmare triggered by the local flora — with a terror known as DARTH VADER!
